name: Meediax
overview:
Meediax.com is a web strategy, design, development, marketing & analytics agency. We provide online solutions that grow clients’ businesses. We provide web design & development, inbound marketing & social media optimisation services to small & medium-sized businesses who are looking to leverage the potentials of the Internet to get a good ROI.

Many businesses do not yet realize what they are missing by not having their presence online. The Internet is the most economic way of doing business these days. At Meediax.com, we ensure that you not only have a presence on the Internet but also ensure that you fully maximize it to your potential growth.
